Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a different perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An imposing wall is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We Detective Boys are going clam digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the elite police detective and\Nyounger brother takes the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I said we should've arrived earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it, there was a major traffic jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an amazing sand castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a masterpiece if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made it happen too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did what little I could and pitched in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so all of you joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten that we're here to gather clams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop monkeying around already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be frank, we've grown tired of it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard we dig, all we got was sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't this better?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't have to force themselves to search for clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like there's a lot around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I beg to differ, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's at least 20 or 30 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you buy them at a fish market or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It so happens that many cheaters will do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a trick to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there's a trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please teach me how!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lightly rake over the beach where waves wash over and soften the sand beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when the waves hit later...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clams come floating up since they're lighter than the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the man, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you learn that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, will we only find clams near the beach shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When clams stick out their siphons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They create tiny holes that people nickname the "clam's eyes".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since clams often aggregate in one place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just look for the spot with a bunch of small holes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And start digging down 10 to 15 centimeters gently so as not to hurt their shells, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't there plenty of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:54.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,CLAM DIGGING WITH A SIGH\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:04:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd they...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those kids are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They keep popping up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge haul, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found more "clam's eyes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we had a bigger rake, wouldn't we be able to get a whole bunch and sell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can even open a seafood store!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:27.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Clam Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge profit right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The width of the rake needs to be under 15 centimeters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And each person shouldn't take more than two kilograms, per proper manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow them and be as happy as a {\i1}clam{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, does everyone really follow the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's imperative that each individual keeps the rules in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, if people were to catch too many eels and reduce their amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preventing you from eating eel rice anymore, wouldn't you hate it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will never allow something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, nobody's in a rush to catch as much as they can, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the original purpose of shellfish gathering is to just have fun finding clams while getting showered in sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone's not having fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he can't find any clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we teach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah,yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what "clam's eyes" are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you dig up those tiny holes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will find this many clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:48.40,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ushigome Tsuguo (21)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've already gotten plenty of clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.40,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why were you sighing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lot has been going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushigome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We bought our lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And snacks too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are these brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your acquaintances?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to bump into these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:22.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Hisazu Shouko (21)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:22.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Yashima Mitsue (20)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,From the same club in our college, called...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mitsuse Takashi (21)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"The Clam Clan," yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, what kind of clan is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The four of you are wearing matching hoodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you guys aiming to become a comedy group?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, it's written on the back of our hoodies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Clam Clan".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Clam Clan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, we are in the same group who love to gather and eat clams...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A clan of four people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, today's the first time we're wearing these hoodies since they were made not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're punning "clam" and "clan"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, let's break for lunch, Ushigome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't forget to buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, your favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushigome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Green tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rice balls with salmon, pollack roe, and plum stuffings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potato chips as a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's our catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've gathered quite a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, isn't this amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow I'm getting hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just eat your boxed lunch, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, to the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we buy some snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're planning to sneakily buy some Yaiba chocolates, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi will go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, all three of you go together as friends'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't buy unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And pay attention to the ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard there was recently a hit-and-run incident in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys really need to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get some eel rice-flavored potato chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't sell such a thing, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should head out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've dug up enough clams, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have a clam party at Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Ushigome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well stay here and clean up our mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you carry the clams to the car and clean out their sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushigome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to run into a restaurant with good shellfish cooking the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why don't we all go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll go, well go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's have lots of drinks at that restaurant tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, crash at Ushigome's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And have the clams we got today for tomorrow's breakfast in some miso soup or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's clean up, clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to sort the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bag is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The plastic bottles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaiba chocolates...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaiba gummies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Yaiba chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought these snacks just because you guys are after the Masked Yaiba freebies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so wrong about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just wanted them so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, that's low!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But those taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, those four who were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did they go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after they finished cleaning up after themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hats off to them for acting properly in contrast to young people these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they forgot one of their important tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how do you know it belongs to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any name written on it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, you can see a fresh, blackened stain on this wooden handle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably a bloodstain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man who let out a sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we first saw him, he was sucking on his index finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So probably he cut his finger on a broken shell or something while digging for clams...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the blood got on the rake handle, is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, they might be looking for it right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When exactly did those four leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, they might still be in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's take it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By "just now," it's already been four or five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they already left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is pretty spacious for a parking lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dropped something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clam digging?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you finished digging, and while the three of you were cleaning up your trash on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went ahead and carried the buckets full of clams to your car—I mean Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when you guys returned to the car, he was already in this state?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An almond scent from his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since next to his body was this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Green tea plastic bottle, what I can surmise is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presumably Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died from drinking a mixture of green tea and cyanide derivatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:14:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Care to shed any light on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seemed to be distraught over something recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he wasn't cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what was troubling him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouko, any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, judging from his state of mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's possible that he committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s suicidal mood as a convenient pretext...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of you doctored this green tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By mixing poison into it, which is another valid possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you insinuating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't do such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which of you bought the green tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of us bought it at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he said he hadn't eaten anything since breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also got some rice balls and snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, did Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} take the green tea out of the plastic bag himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I handed it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But soon after that, he was gulping it down as if nothing was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did any of you touch the plastic bottle while he was drinking from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time we may have touched it was when we bought it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} held onto it the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unlikely that anyone else touched it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I merely passed the rice balls over to Ushigome by throwing it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rice balls with salmon, pollack roe, and plum stuffings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did open the bag of potato chips and place it next to him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never touched the green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One could've done it when the others weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What those people are saying is all true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} unscrewed the cap, no one other than Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Runt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you with that Smoking Kogorou before or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Smoking"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sleeping!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, is that private detective with a small mustache here also?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In his stead, my friends tagged along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We brought the professor here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, you tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was holding his green tea bottle the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think he let anyone else handle his tea while he was drinking it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't take your eyes off him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although today was the first time the children and I came across him at this beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw him let out a deep sigh, so we were concerned a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A deep sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Near the feet of the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found this small jar lying around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the fact that someone replaced the pills with powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is the cyanide substance in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jar Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} used to hold his supplement pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I often saw him taking those.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forensics!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Examine this jar along with the plastic bottle and the lid if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, you runts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you recall anything else that might help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you laugh a bit for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,COME AGAIN!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you looked just like that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like a certain coral-haired police officer we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Howdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise he looks like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this person is the younger brother of that Inspector Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do recall my brother telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About how that Smoking Kogorou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Sleeping, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a brat with glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A brat with glasses"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some runts who like to play detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Used to hang out together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although their faces and voices are similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their ways of speech and tempers are complete opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell you this, but looks like well have no further use of your little detective group this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one else touched the plastic bottle in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the container with a substance resembling poison was found inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention he was so depressed that he kept sighing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to deem it a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So,shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brats go home, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the rush, "younger brother"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that cap really belong to that plastic bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since only this little guy was in the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the tea residue on the inside of the cap hasn't dried yet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the brand is a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's blood around the mouth of the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I see nothing of that sort on the cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, why is there blood on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} injured his finger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, he probably cut himself on a broken shell or something while picking up clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he was picking those up while having a lot on his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's most likely true that he was injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since when we first met him, he was sucking on his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we realized the rake with blood that was forgotten on the beach belonged to that chubby mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when we came to return it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We encountered this scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He does have a cut on his right index finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the blood already clotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So basically, when he first unscrewed the cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that his wound hadn't closed resulted in his blood getting on it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when he brought the bottle with him here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He noticed the blood on the cap just as he was about to open it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he wiped off the blood before opening it, and that's what transpired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would a person who's about to commit suicide do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's an ill bird that fouls its own nest".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he wanted to keep it clean before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm waiting for the forensics report
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, I'll have to ask you guys to be on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
